"{\"uid\": \"wnd.com-2024-04-olympic-gold-medalist-lives-life-joyfully-even-3rd-brain-tumor-diagnosis\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"ByAround the Web  April 20, 2024    (FOX NEWS) - Former American figure skater Scott Hamilton dedicated his early life to his sport.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 64, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999991429780528, \"rank\": 5.964260170027108e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 93, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hamilton_(musician)\", \"score\": 0.6185835445245889, \"rank\": 0.6081517352703515, \"text\": \"Scott Hamilton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hamilton_(musician)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hamilton_(musician)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was rewarded with an incredible winning streak in the early 1980s that saw him win four consecutive U.S. titles and four consecutive world championships.\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He never lost between 1981 and 1984, and his hard work culminated in a gold medal performance at the 1984 Winter Olympics.\", \"from\": 290, \"to\": 412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Howerver, Hamilton, now 65, has dedicated his post-Olympic life towards a new goal - funding cancer research with the hope of giving people the chance at \\\"a second life,\\\" an opportunity he was given many times over.\", \"from\": 414, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 424, \"end\": 432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 8.819734640599749e-13, \"text\": \"Hamilton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Get the hottest, most important news stories on the Internet - delivered FREE to your inbox as soon as they break!\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 745, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Take just 30 seconds and sign up for WND's Email News Alerts!\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 783, \"end\": 786, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"WND\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/WorldNetDaily\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hamilton opened up about his personal battles with cancer and how his mother's death at just 18 shaped his mindset early on in an interview with Fox News Digital.\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 971, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 809, \"end\": 817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 8.819734640599749e-13, \"text\": \"Hamilton\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 954, \"end\": 962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.9999999892224879, \"rank\": 1.0760468540547233e-08, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was given a chance to skate, and I had to figure out how to do it at a high level,\\\" Hamilton said.\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hamilton_Academical_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999999999988631, \"rank\": 8.819734640599749e-13, \"t